title: Phillips, Craig And Dean Discography 1992-2014 (21 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
PHILLIPS, CRAIG AND DEAN DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 21 releases...

 * 1992 - Phillips, Craig And Dean
 * 1994 - Lifeline
 * 1995 - Trust
 * 1996 - Repeat The Sounding Joy
 * 1997 - Where Strength Begins
 * 1998 - Favorite Songs Of All
 * 1999 - Restoration
 * 2001 - Let My Words Be Few
 * 2003 - Let Your Glory Fall
 * 2004 - Let The Worshippers Arise
 * 2005 - The Worship Collection
 * 2006 - The Ultimate Collection
 * 2006 - Top Of My Lungs
 * 2008 - Greatest Hits
 * 2009 - Discover 6 Essential Songs
 * 2009 - Fearless
 * 2009 - Revelation Song - Single
 * 2012 - Breathe In
 * 2012 - When The Stars Burn Down - Single
 * 2013 - Hope For All The World
 * 2014 - Above It All

Phillips, Craig and Dean are a contemporary Christian music trio composed of Randy Phillips, Shawn Craig, and Dan Dean.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - December 2014
